  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "ベルトモント家の呪いが再び襲いかかる、ゲームボーイ用の第二の「キャッスルヴァニア」冒険。 このゲームは、初めてのモノクロ冒険から15年後の物語です。クリストファーの息子が行方不明になり、4つの神秘的な城が霧の中から現れました。彼はそれぞれの城に旅し、そこで出会う悪魔を打ち倒して息子を救わなければなりません。もしかすると、ドラキュラは私たちが思っていたよりも死んでいないのかもしれません。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "Fifteen years after vanquishing the emperor of evil, Count Dracula, Christopher Belmont now faces a vampire swearing vengeance. Drac's back. And he's turned your son, Soleiyu Belmont, into a deadly demon to do his dirty deeds. Now not only do you have to rescue your kid from the Count's clutches, you have to first track him down in four creep packed Castles. Fortunately, you posses weapons like armor piercing Battle Axes, beast burning Holy Water, and the Legendary Mystic Whip. And you can increase your arsenal with power up items like Crystal Balls, Hearts, and Candles. Strap on your shield and step into the shadows. That is, if you're prepared for the dwellers of darkness.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
